        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-700">Neon-pastel glow, soft edges, generous comfort.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 bg-dystopia-300/60 border border-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Dystopia</h3>
